  <section id="stages">
    <h2>The 5 Stages of Strength & Aesthetic Mastery</h2>

    <div class="stage">
      <h3>Stage 1: Foundations</h3>
      <p>Learn the core principles of hypertrophy and progressive overload. Establish proper form, consistency, and understand the basics of protein intake, sleep, and total volume.</p>
      <a class="cta" href="#">Start With the Basics</a>
    </div>

    <div class="stage">
      <h3>Stage 2: Progressive Builder</h3>
      <p>Advance to structured routines, logbook tracking, and split training. Learn to manipulate sets, reps, and rest periods for optimized growth.</p>
      <a class="cta" href="#">Get the 4-Day Builder Plan</a>
    </div>

    <div class="stage">
      <h3>Stage 3: Precision Phase</h3>
      <p>Unlock training intensity with RPE, tempo control, and progressive overload cycles. Dial in macronutrients, sleep hygiene, and recovery to avoid plateaus.</p>
      <a class="cta" href="#">Download the Precision Toolkit</a>
    </div>

    <div class="stage">
      <h3>Stage 4: Specialization</h3>
      <p>Focus on weak points with advanced techniques like supersets, pre-exhaustion, and mesocycle programming. Tailor training blocks to target lagging body parts.</p>
      <a class="cta" href="#">Unlock Your Specialization Guide</a>
    </div>

    <div class="stage">
      <h3>Stage 5: Mastery</h3>
      <p>Combine all previous stages into a cohesive yearly plan. Monitor long-term progression, use deloading strategically, and align your training with your life goals.</p>
      <a class="cta" href="#">Apply for 1-on-1 Coaching</a>
    </div>
  </section>

